Public - CMS


GET
/api/public/announcements/
Get announcements & news


Returns active announcements. Results are paginated (default 20/page).

Filter: ?category=announcement or ?category=news

Pagination: ?page=1&page_size=20 (max 100)

Send X-Language: ml to get Malayalam text where available.

Results are Redis-cached (24h). Cache is cleared automatically on admin writes.

Parameters
Cancel
No parameters

Execute
Clear
